name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Tabmark - Organize Your Tabs and Bookmarks

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The best way to organize your Chrome tabs and bookmarks.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Do you have too many tabs open in your browser? Tabmark allows you to organize and bookmark your favorite web pages and easily bring them up whenever needed.
